headline: Freeport Provides Update on Restart Plans for Grasberg Minerals District
summary: PHOENIX, November 18, 2025--Freeport (NYSE: FCX) announced today plans to restore large-scale production from PT Freeport Indonesia’s (PTFI) Grasberg operations in Central Papua, Indonesia.
